# Strings

```scalascript
val s = "Hello, World!"
println(s.length)
println(s.toUpperCase)
println(s.toLowerCase)
println(s.contains("World"))
println(s.startsWith("Hello"))
println(s.endsWith("!"))
println(s.replace("World", "Scala"))
val name = "ScalaScript"
println(s"Language: $name")
println(s.take(5))
println(s.drop(7))
```
